trigger
= = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = =

The "trigger" command is not intended to be used by end users;
it's what the mj_trigger utility uses to kick off periodic functions.


For a list of all help topics send this one-line message
   help topics
to the server at $MJ
